---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact Hummingbird Social Studio | Wedding Template Questions & Custom Requests"
  description="Contact Hummingbird Social Studio with questions about editable wedding templates, bridal shower invitations, printable stationery, custom design requests, and digital template support."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <h1>Have a question about a template or custom idea?</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Reach out with questions about wedding invitation templates, bridal
        shower invitations, printing, editing, matching stationery pieces, or
        custom design requests.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Template Questions</h2>
        <p>
          Need help choosing the right invitation suite, understanding what is
          editable, or figuring out whether a template will work for your event?
          Send a quick note and include the design or collection you are looking
          at.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Printing Help</h2>
        <p>
          If you are unsure about paper weight, envelope size, online printing,
          or whether to print at home or through a local shop, the studio can
          point you in the right direction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Custom Requests</h2>
        <p>
          Love the Hummingbird Social Studio style but need a different size,
          matching sign, custom wording layout, or coordinated event piece?
          Custom design requests are welcome.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature-band">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Email the Studio</p>
      <h2>The easiest way to get in touch is by email.</h2>
      <p>
        For template questions, printing help, collaboration ideas, or custom
        stationery requests, send an email with as much detail as possible.
      </p>

      <p>
        Helpful details to include:
      </p>

      <ul class="list">
        <li>The template, product, or collection you are interested in</li>
        <li>Your event type and date</li>
        <li>Any wording, size, color, or layout changes you need</li>
        <li>Whether you plan to print at home, locally, or online</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="button-row">
        <a class="button" href="mailto:gradualgrowthonline@gmail.com">
          Email Hummingbird Social Studio
        </a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/custom-design-requests/">
          Request a Custom Design
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Before You Reach Out</p>
      <h2>Looking for a quick answer?</h2>
      <p>
        Many common questions are answered in the template support pages. These
        guides can help you understand how editable templates work, where to
        print them, and what to expect after purchase.
      </p>

      <div class="button-row">
        <a class="button" href="/how-it-works/">How It Works</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/printing-guide/">Printing Guide</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/faq/">FAQ</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
